<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jordana Brewster put her own spin on country chic when she stepped out in Los Angeles this Tuesday for some takeout.</p>

<p>The 40-year-old slipped into a set of pink overalls, tying a denim jacket around her waist and slinging on a wicker handbag.</p>

<p>She made sure to take the precaution of wearing a face mask as she emerged amid the coronavirus pandemic, opting for a gigham covering.</p>

<p>Sizzling sensation: Jordana Brewster put her own spin on country chic when she stepped out in Los Angeles this Tuesday for some takeout</p>

<p>Jordana rose to fame as a soap star and has been a mainstay in the Fast And The Furious franchise as Mia Toretto.</p>

<p>She will feature in the upcoming installment F9 which was meant to come out this May but has been bumped to next April by the coronavirus lockdowns.</p>

<p>The sizzling sensation is now dating ValueAct Capital CEO Mason Morfit and was seen kissing him at the beach in July.</p>

<p>Her romance with Mason went public in mid-July just weeks after she filed for divorce from her husband Andrew Form after 13 years of marriage.</p>

<p>Hoofing it: The 40-year-old slipped into a set of pink overalls, tying a denim jacket around her waist and slinging on a wicker handbag</p>

<p>Jordana and her film producer ex share two sons, a six-year-old called Julian and a four-year-old called Rowan.</p>

<p>They became an item through her 2006 film The Texas Chainsaw Massacre: The Beginning, which on which Andrew was a producer.</p>

<p>'We started dating in secret - you know, hanging out in my trailer - because it would have been unprofessional otherwise,' she spilled to InStyle later.</p>

<p>The way they were: Earlier this year she filed for divorce from her husband Andrew Form after 13 years of marriage; they are pictured out in Los Angeles last June</p>

<p>He proposed on the one-year anniversary of their relationship and presented her with a 3.2 carat engagement ring.</p>

<p>Six months after he popped the question the couple married on the Caribbean island Nevis, according to People magazine.</p>

<p>After their split a People source said: 'They have the utmost respect for each other. They remain committed to lovingly co-parent their two children as a team.'</p>
